{
  "stem": "20035.4",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I tossed that dish towards my brother when the SS guard, for unknown reason, instead of using his gun he used the butt of his rifle, and hit me in the back, two or three times and asked me to spit it out.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Naturally, I did not spit out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I swallowed as much as I could.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I found out way later, that the time when he hit me, he broke one of my vertebrae.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But there is no such thing as being sick and no such a thing as not being able to do.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because if you stayed sick the next-- next day you didn't live.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But the people in our group, et cetera, they knew that I can't lift.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Once it was already up on the shoulder I could walk.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But bending down and lift, for a couple of weeks it was hard.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the camaraderie was unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And not only camaraderie.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Everybody knew if you have to help somebody, you help somebody.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But by there already, many, many times.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I mean, it was a-- practically daily affair, that when from your group of six, sometimes somebody didn't move.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they supposed to turn.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Or somebody ordered to turn.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And just the person was dead.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And bodies started to pile, and-- and respect-- or I would say that not respect, because we respected life.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But you know, it was an accepted fact that people die, that people cannot take it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And people are getting to the point where physically, mentally, but mostly physically, there they-- here we had only barbed wire.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We had no electrical wire around it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But it wasn't required.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "The march was long.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
